					<li>
										Teaching at UCI <br>(2006 - present)
										<li>

											<a href="#">Requirements Engineering and Analysis</a></li>

											<!---<li><font size="1">
											Aims to equip students to develop techniques of software-intensive systems through successful
											requirements analysis techniques and requirements engineering. Students learn systematic process of
											developing requirements through co-operative problem analysis, representation, and validation.-->

										<li>
											<a href="#">Introduction to Software Engineering</a></li>
